content: So I won't be able to make it today -- it seems like we've not had a lot of energy here -- I propose we cancel this weekly meeting and roll any book related updates into the standard meeting?
I feel like i've basically just been giving updates about what I've been doing. If there are other folks who find that useful, let me know, but otherwise I won't bug people about it.
I'd like to see updates :) I'd also like to circle back to the book. I've blocked out some time to spend on async stuff every week (which I didn't have before), so i'm hoping to do more of that.
But I guess we don't need a meeting to do that
